Which command can be used to determine the current time- zone setting while trouble-shooting a time- zone configuration issue?
A)  timedatectl status
B)  timedate - - gettz
C)  tzdata - - list
D)  timezone - - show
A
A. The command timedatectl status shows the current time zone along with otherinformation about time and date on the device. The other commands shown are not valid forthis purpose.
